00:30:29.450 --> 00:30:32.300
WebXR that you might have
heard about at the previous I/O

00:30:32.300 --> 00:30:33.840
session.

00:30:33.840 --> 00:30:35.810
WebXR means that
you can experience

00:30:35.810 --> 00:30:39.292
VR content in your browser
using any VR headset.

