00:30:44.640 --> 00:30:48.240
to the web is that you
can easily embed them.

00:30:48.240 --> 00:30:50.522
Just go to Poly, click
on a Share button,

00:30:50.522 --> 00:30:52.230
and you'll get an
iFrame snippet that you

00:30:52.230 --> 00:30:55.015
can put in any blog or website.

00:30:55.015 --> 00:30:56.390
And when you think
about it, this

00:30:56.390 --> 00:30:59.069
can be truly transformational
for business.

