00:35:19.385 --> 00:35:21.510
I can't really think about
education and technology

00:35:21.510 --> 00:35:24.610
without thinking about
this guy, Seymour Papert.

00:35:24.610 --> 00:35:26.320
20 years ago, he
observed that it

00:35:26.320 --> 00:35:29.320
might be time to reconsider our
fundamental conception of what

00:35:29.320 --> 00:35:30.610
