to use technology

00:35:55.740 --> 00:35:59.610
to lower these barriers to
make learning richer, less

00:35:59.610 --> 00:36:01.950
abstract, to make all
that important reading

00:36:01.950 --> 00:36:03.660
and writing that
we do be augmented

00:36:03.660 --> 00:36:06.420
with the actual parts of the
world that they refer to.

00:36:06.420 --> 00:36:09.050
