sounds, 3D objects,

00:36:09.050 --> 00:36:12.950
simulations, all the formats
immersive computing enables,

00:36:12.950 --> 00:36:14.810
to give learners
more effective entry

00:36:14.810 --> 00:36:19.234
points into complicated
subjects and ideas.

